nodes.text: Tam Uliss was a squat, muscular Human male from Corellia, living on Ansion in 22 BBY.[source?] The industrialist supported Ansion's attempt to secede from the Old Republic, meeting secretly with conspirators in a Quadrant H-46 cantina and an orbiting transport above Coruscant. After the attempt failed, he was killed by Shu Mai, dropped from Bror Tower Three onto the surface of Coruscant.
